msgid ""
"Event Scheduler for:\n"
"  - Event: %(event_name)s (%(event_id)s)\n"
"  - Scheduled: %(date)s\n"
"  - Template: %(template_name)s (%(template_id)s)\n"
"\n"
"Failed with error:\n"
"  - %(error)s\n"
"\n"
"You receive this email because you are:\n"
"  - the organizer of the event,\n"
"  - or the responsible of the event,\n"
"  - or the last writer of the template.\n"
msgstr ""
"ເຄື່ອງມືຕັ້ງເວລາສຳລັບ:\n"
"  - ງານ: %(event_name)s (%(event_id)s)\n"
"  - ເວລາທີ່ກຳນົດ: %(date)s\n"
"  - ແມ່ແບບ: %(template_name)s (%(template_id)s)\n"
"\n"
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ:\n"
"  - %(error)s\n"
"\n"
"ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບອີເມວນີ້ຍ້ອນທ່ານແມ່ນ:\n"
"  - ຜູ້ຈັດງານ,\n"
"  - ຫຼື ຜູ້ຮັບຜິດຊອບງານ,\n"
"  - ຫຼື ຜູ້ແກ້ໄຂແມ່ແບບລ້າສຸດ.\n"

